- Second Layer (Top): 1 yellow rectangular block, 1 yellow curved block, 1 green rectangular block, 1 orange angled block

5. Green Rectangular Block (Block 6): 1 time
6. Orange Angled Block (Block 15): 1 time

Assembly Instructions:

    Step2: Move block with index 8 (orange cylinder)
